  p Welcome to #[em QuoteApp], a very basic Express website developed as a platform for Database, TDD and Travis/CI/CD Training

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Quotes:] !{data.quote_count}
     
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Categories:] !{data.category_count}